all the trauma and fear

00:26:38.310 --> 00:26:41.620 align:middle line:84%
that's running through my
body when that's taking place.

00:26:41.620 --> 00:26:44.350 align:middle line:84%
And as I started to
use tapping on it,

00:26:44.350 --> 00:26:45.630 align:middle line:90%
the memory started to come.

00:26:45.630 --> 00:26:48.330 align:middle line:84%
And it was the very first
time I actually got my memory

00:26:48.330 --> 00:26:50.430 align:middle line:90%
back around what happened.

00:26:50.430 --> 00:26:53.100 align:middle line:84%
And probably for
about six months

00:26:53.100 --> 00:26:57.690 align:middle line:84%
I did continual work on that
and pulled out so many layers.

00:26:57.690 --> 00:27:00.630 align:middle line:84%
And more and more
memories kept unfolding.

00:27:00.630 --> 00:27:03.420 align:middle line:84%
And more and more love was
brought to those memories.

00:27:03.420 --> 00:27:05.550 align:middle line:84%
And all of the fear that
was trapped in my system

00:27:05.550 --> 00:27:07.080 align:middle line:90%
started to dissolve.

00:27:07.080 --> 00:27:10.470 align:middle line:84%
And those reactions that I would
have in the middle of the night

00:27:10.470 --> 00:27:11.640 align:middle line:90%
stopped.

00:27:11.640 --> 00:27:13.515 align:middle line:84%
And I became more
peaceful inside.

00:27:13.515 --> 00:27:18.540 align:middle line:90%


00:27:18.540 --> 00:27:21.730 align:middle line:84%
>> There's so much anger
and judgment present when

00:27:21.730 --> 00:27:23.630 align:middle line:84%
the trauma has not
been addressed.

00:27:23.630 --> 00:27:26.080 align:middle line:84%
So they're not ready
to even entertain

00:27:26.080 --> 00:27:28.780 align:middle line:84%
