what they did, or their mother

00:27:28.780 --> 00:27:30.020 align:middle line:90%
did what they did.

00:27:30.020 --> 00:27:32.520 align:middle line:84%
But when they can start to heal
the trauma within themselves

00:27:32.520 --> 00:27:34.210 align:middle line:84%
separated from the
individual, and they

00:27:34.210 --> 00:27:37.330 align:middle line:84%
