or that you may regret.

00:38:46.390 --> 00:38:49.150 align:middle line:84%
It's really important to
acknowledge that feeling it

00:38:49.150 --> 00:38:51.890 align:middle line:84%
is actually a faster track
way to get through it.

00:38:51.890 --> 00:38:53.300 align:middle line:90%
Don't hide from it.

00:38:53.300 --> 00:38:55.690 align:middle line:84%
Find a way to work
through it and acknowledge

00:38:55.690 --> 00:39:00.640 align:middle line:84%
that sometimes it's so bad
you got nothing but tears.

00:39:00.640 --> 00:39:05.470 align:middle line:84%
>> The amount of energy it takes
to hide and suppress any type

00:39:05.470 --> 00:39:09.120 align:middle line:90%
of trauma is staggering.

00:39:09.120 --> 00:39:11.350 align:middle line:84%
And we're living with
it every single day

00:39:11.350 --> 00:39:12.760 align:middle line:90%
