00:39:12.760 --> 00:39:16.410 align:middle line:84%
And I believe that the cost,
the short-term discomfort,

00:39:16.410 --> 00:39:18.160 align:middle line:84%
if you want to call
it that, of addressing

00:39:18.160 --> 00:39:21.550 align:middle line:84%
a trauma, such as sexual abuse,
physical abuse, mental abuse

00:39:21.550 --> 00:39:27.180 align:middle line:84%
that you experienced as a
child, the short-term discomfort

00:39:27.180 --> 00:39:29.780 align:middle line:84%
it's the tip of the iceberg
when it comes to living

00:39:29.780 --> 00:39:31.430 align:middle line:90%
with that every single day.

00:39:31.430 --> 00:39:35.480 align:middle line:84%
Because, again, your
soul is depressed.

00:39:35.480 --> 00:39:37.370 align:middle line:90%
Your spirit is squashed.

00:39:37.370 --> 00:39:39.650 align:middle line:84%
You don't get to amplify
you don't get to show up.

00:39:39.650 --> 00:39:41.750 align:middle line:84%
You don't get to share
all of who you are.

00:39:41.750 --> 00:39:47.463 align:middle line:84%
And if you think for a moment
that by me hiding my trauma,

00:39:47.463 --> 00:39:49.880 align:middle line:84%
by me not talking about it,
I'm protecting everybody else.

00:39:49.880 --> 00:39:51.410 align:middle line:90%
You're living in a cloud.

00:39:51.410 --> 00:39:53.780 align:middle line:90%
You're living on Mars.

00:39:53.780 --> 00:39:57.410 align:middle line:84%
Because your kids are feeling it
energetically every single day.

00:39:57.410 --> 00:39:58.940 align:middle line:84%
They're not sitting
there going, why

00:39:58.940 --> 00:40:03.612 align:middle line:84%
